IMAPAccount hostinger
Host imap.hostinger.com
User mail@david-star.com
PassCmd "pass email/hostinger"
TLSType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN

IMAPStore hostinger-remote
Account hostinger

MaildirStore hostinger-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/Mail/
Inbox ~/Mail/INBOX

Channel hostinger
Far :hostinger-remote:
Near :hostinger-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
SyncState *
